@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="sub-layout-div">

    <div class="container">

        <div class="">
            <h1 class="pt-5">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        </div>

        <div>
            <p class="py-3"><b>Effective Date:</b> 01-01-2025</p>
            <p class="privacy-p ml-0 mb-5">Welcome to Amla Marketplace. Your trust is our priority, and we are committed to safeguarding your privacy and ensuring a respectful, secure environment for all users. By using our platform, you agree to adhere to the policies outlined below.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-div">
            <div>
                <h4>1. Respectful and Appropriate Content.</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="privacy-p">
                <ul>
                    <li>Users are strictly prohibited from uploading, listing, or sharing offensive, harmful, or inappropriate products, images, descriptions, or names.</li>
                    <li>Content that is discriminatory, obscene, defamatory, or violates any laws or company standards is not allowed and will be removed.</li>
                    <li>Users found violating this policy may face account suspension or permanent removal from the platform.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-div">
            <div>
                <h4>2. Data Privacy and Security</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="privacy-p">
                <ul>
                    <li>Amla Marketplace collects and processes only the necessary personal information required to operate the platform efficiently.</li>
                    <li>We implement advanced security measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, misuse, or disclosure.</li>
                    <li>User account information, including passwords and sensitive details, is encrypted and securely stored.</li>
                    <li>We do not sell, share, or trade user data with third parties without explicit consent, except where required by law.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-div">
            <div>
                <h4>3. Responsible Selling and Buying</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="privacy-p">
                <ul>
                    <li>All products uploaded must comply with our platform’s standards and approval process.</li>
                    <li>Products that are fraudulent, counterfeit, or unsafe are strictly prohibited.</li>
                    <li>Sellers must provide accurate product descriptions, pricing, and inventory details.</li>
                    <li>Buyers are encouraged to report suspicious or inappropriate listings to our support team.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-div">
            <div>
                <h4>4. Admin Oversight</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="privacy-p">
                <ul>
                    <li>All uploaded content is subject to review and approval by our dedicated admin team to ensure compliance with platform guidelines.</li>
                    <li>Admins reserve the right to reject or remove any content that violates our policies or poses a risk to our community.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-div">
            <div>
                <h4>5. User Accountability</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="privacy-p">
                <ul>
                    <li>Users are responsible for the accuracy of the information they provide and the content they upload.</li>
                    <li>Misuse of the platform, including fraudulent activities, will lead to immediate action.</li>
                    <li>Respectful communication is required at all times; harassment or inappropriate behavior towards other users or admins will not be tolerated.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-div">
            <div>
                <h4>6. Continuous Improvement</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="privacy-p">
                <ul>
                    <li>Our privacy policy and platform guidelines are subject to periodic updates to align with legal standards and community feedback.</li>
                    <li>Users will be notified of any significant changes to this policy.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>            
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-div">
            <div>
                <h4>7. Contact Us</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="privacy-p">
                <p>
                    If you have questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at [Insert Support Email].</br>

                    Thank you for being a part of Amla Marketplace, where collaboration and respect drive our community forward.
                </p>
            </div>            
        </div>
    </div>

</div>